-- Usmanov May Pay $5 Billion to Gain Control of MegaFon, RBC Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-04-01T16:09:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-01/usmanov-may-pay-5-billion-to-gain-control-of-megafon-rbc-says.html
Russian billionaire Alisher Usmanov
may buy Mikhail Fridman’s stake in cell-phone operator OAO
MegaFon for about $5 billion to gain control over the company,
RBC Daily said in a preview of its articles to be published
tomorrow.  Yuliya Mazanova, spokeswoman for Usmanov in Moscow, didn’t
immediately respond to a call to her mobile phone outside of
regular business hours.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Khrennikov in Moscow at 
 ikhrennikov@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
John Viljoen at 
 jviljoen@bloomberg.net  